Feature: Authentication    Scenario: Successful login     Given I am an existing user     When I visit the login page     And I enter my valid credentials     And I click 'Login'     Then I should be logged in     And I should see my dashboard    Scenario: Login with invalid credentials     Given I visit the login page       When I enter invalid credentials     And I click 'Login'     Then I should see an 'Invalid email or password' error     And I should not be logged in    Scenario: Logging out     Given I am logged in     When I click 'Logout'       Then I should be logged out     And I should be redirected to the login page    Scenario: Accessing protected page while logged out     Given I am not logged in     When I attempt to access a protected page     Then I should be redirected to the login page     And I should see an 'Please log in' message